1
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,430
Sorry!

2
00:00:15,430 --> 00:00:17,230
Miss Lu, you finally arrived.

3
00:00:17,230 --> 00:00:18,870
Dr. Gu has been waiting for you.

4
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:19,440
Okay!

5
00:01:55,410 --> 00:01:58,580
[Shadow Detective]

6
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:01,160
[Episode 5]

7
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,760
[Maintain Law and Discipline]

8
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,890
These are my findings in the hospital.

9
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,800
I've also verified the facts
with Mei from the nursing home.

10
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,490
Liu Jialiang and Zhou Yongjie

11
00:02:09,509 --> 00:02:11,910
did embezzle all the charitable funds
meant for the nursing home.

12
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:13,240
Even the donations specifically

13
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,380
directed to each elderly resident

14
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,640
were taken away by them

15
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,430
through intimidation, fraud,

16
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:19,560
and even threats of violence.

17
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,590
This is known to all in the nursing home.

18
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:23,800
Angry though people are,
they keep silent out of fear.

19
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,000
What's your opinion?

20
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,910
After compiling the information
from various sources,

21
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:29,190
I made the following deductions.

22
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:31,030
The deceased,
Liu Jialiang and Zhou Yongjie,

23
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:33,740
were well acquainted with each other
as friends.

24
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:35,240
They went to a casino together

25
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,430
in the hope of making a fortune
by cheating.

26
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:39,660
Unexpectedly, they were caught in the act.

27
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,020
Then, Long turned his back on them.

28
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,560
Liu and Zhou ended up owing massive debts.

29
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,690
To pay off the debts,

30
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,430
they started

31
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,030
targeting the nursing home.

32
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:50,190
Liu Jialiang even confined his own mother

33
00:02:50,210 --> 00:02:52,140
in an attempt to extort more money.

34
00:02:52,350 --> 00:02:53,840
Therefore, we have grounds for suspicion

35
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,380
that the killer of Liu and Zhou

36
00:02:55,380 --> 00:02:57,380
is connected with the nursing home.

37
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:01,680
That doesn't sound right.

38
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:04,280
Most of those in the nursing home
are elderly people

39
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,520
who can barely walk steadily.

40
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,870
How could any of them have possibly
committed two murders in a row?

41
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,630
I know it sounds unbelievable.

42
00:03:10,550 --> 00:03:12,510
Nut based on the evidence
found at the scenes

43
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:13,630
and the information we have,

44
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,290
this is a strong possibility.

45
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,560
First,
they had sufficient motive for murder.

46
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,190
Second,

47
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,710
we found large amounts

48
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:21,930
of sedatives in the victims' bodies,

49
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,240
which means the killer took their lives

50
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,400
when they were incapacitated.

51
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,560
Under those circumstances,

52
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,420
anyone could carry out a killing.

53
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,360
So, the killer could be

54
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:33,070
a staffer in the nursing home.

55
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:33,630
Correct.

56
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,520
Take Mei as an example.

57
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:37,360
She knows the dark secrets
about the nursing home,

58
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,280
and she suffered for a long time

59
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,590
under the oppression of Liu and Zhou.

60
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:42,450
Even people like Mei
can't be ruled out as suspects.

61
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,150
I agree with her.

62
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,780
Now, let's divide tasks.

63
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,800
It's time to conduct background checks
on the social ties

64
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,960
of everyone in the nursing home.

65
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,460
Yes.

66
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,010
Got it.

67
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,800
Hello, this is the Police Station.

68
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,430
What?

69
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,010
The victim, Lin Xuehui, 38 years old,

70
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:22,010
was a typist at Huating Trading Company.

71
00:04:22,010 --> 00:04:24,300
Her body was discovered
by the restaurant chef's apprentice,

72
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,830
as he opened the door.

73
00:04:26,010 --> 00:04:27,660
The restaurant owner
had a banquet scheduled

74
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,680
for a celebration today.

75
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,080
However, this happened.

76
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,800
Have those who have keys
to the kitchen been inquired?

77
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,360
Yes.

78
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,730
The owner, the chef, and the apprentice

79
00:04:38,730 --> 00:04:39,659
all have alibis.

80
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:42,190
The victim was scalded to death.

81
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:43,750
Also,

82
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,870
in the same spot on her forehead,

83
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:47,630
there is the same mark

84
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,320
as the previous two victims.

85
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:51,920
Could she have been killed
by the same person?

86
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,600
Lu Yizhen,

87
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,560
what's your opinion?

88
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,800
There's no sign of struggle

89
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,200
or fighting at the scene.

90
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:03,310
It couldn't have been easy to scald

91
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,720
a living person to death,

92
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:07,830
unless the victim had become unconscious

93
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,980
before she was put into the water.

94
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,680
That is to say,

95
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,680
just like the previous two victims,

96
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:15,430
Lin Xuehui was given a large dose
of sedatives before she died.

97
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:15,950
Yes.

98
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,010
Whether she took sedatives or not

99
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:19,270
can only be determined

100
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,430
after an autopsy.

101
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:21,780
Inspector,

102
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:24,240
this time, you might be dealing with

103
00:05:25,290 --> 00:05:26,220
a serial killer.

104
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:26,800
[East Asia Hotel]

105
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,390
My daughter

106
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:29,070
is in there!

107
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:31,870
Please show some understanding.
I'm begging you.

108
00:05:32,090 --> 00:05:33,680
There are officers coming out.

109
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,280
Officers,

110
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,270
please let us in.

111
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,510
Officer, my daughter is in there.

112
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:40,390
Please let me see her.

113
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:40,870
Please.

114
00:05:41,270 --> 00:05:42,800
You can't go inside, ma'am.

115
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,790
As the victim's next of kin,

116
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:46,820
you'll be traumatized by the scene.

117
00:05:46,870 --> 00:05:48,140
My condolences, ma'am.

118
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,030
Trust us.

119
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:51,920
We'll find the killer as soon as possible,
alright?

120
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,810
Tell me...

121
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,040
How...

122
00:05:55,850 --> 00:05:58,440
How exactly did my daughter die?

123
00:05:58,470 --> 00:06:00,470
Ma'am, what happened to your leg?

124
00:06:02,790 --> 00:06:04,520
It was scalded by hot water.

125
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,800
How did it happen?

126
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,930
When I was making tea, a cup of hot water

127
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,000
accidentally spilled on my leg.

128
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:15,100
I don't think a cup of hot tea
could cause such an injury.

129
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:17,750
It...

130
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,610
Do you know how your daughter died?

131
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,120
How?

132
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,240
She was scalded to death in a barrel.

133
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,390
My daughter...

134
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:31,550
Why are you still withholding the truth

135
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:32,670
at a time like this?

136
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,510
Officers, let me tell you the story.

137
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,600
Given her poor health,

138
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,190
this old lady can't find a job.

139
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:41,720
Her daughter found her a nuisance

140
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,330
and yelled at her every day.

141
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:44,480
She got that leg injury

142
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:47,340
when her daughter poured
a glass of hot water on her!

143
00:06:49,370 --> 00:06:51,380
What a poor thing.

144
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:55,490
[Shanghai Police Station]

145
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:02,410
Inspector.

146
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:17,100
[Beware, danger!]

147
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,430
Conference time!

148
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:20,830
When we last visited

149
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,160
Zhou Yongjie's father,

150
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:22,920
did you notice

151
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,750
there was something off with his hands?

152
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,920
Yes, I did. Why do you ask?

153
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,450
Do you find him suspicious?

154
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,660
Take a look at this.

155
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,950
[The victim pleaded for leniency nonstop,
so the assailant was set free]

156
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:37,120
Zhou Yongjie beat his father
and broke his bones?

157
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,360
We meant to arrest Zhou Yongjie,

158
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,830
but his father kept begging for mercy.

159
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:41,070
In the end, the case was dropped.

160
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,530
Only this record was left.

161
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,120
Any thoughts?

162
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:52,090
All the three murder victims
were involved in elder abuse.

163
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:54,040
Lin Xuehui scalded her mother,

164
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,800
so she was scalded to death.

165
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,430
Zhou Yongjie broke his father's bones

166
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:00,190
by brutal assaults,

167
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,480
so he died from severe injuries

168
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,940
caused by bone fractures.

169
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,510
Liu Jialiang confined

170
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:06,510
his mother in the attic

171
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:08,310
and starved her

172
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,100
for a long time.

173
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:12,030
So, the killer planned for him
to be starved to death.

174
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,160
These three people

175
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,390
were tortured to death
in the same extreme manners

176
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:17,630
as they abused their parents

177
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,950
when they were alive.

178
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,160
That's a merely passable answer.

179
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,680
Dr. Ding informed me just now

180
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,800
that a large amount of sedatives

181
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,510
was found in Lin Xuehui's body,

182
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,510
just like the previous two victims.

183
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:30,070
The murders respectively happened
at a park entrance,

184
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:30,850
a garbage dump,

185
00:08:30,850 --> 00:08:32,200
and a restaurant kitchen,

186
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,799
where dead bodies
could be easily discovered.

187
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:36,210
It means the killer

188
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:38,570
had no intention
to conceal his criminal acts.

189
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:39,960
Instead, he wanted them to be revealed.

190
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,220
That's a possibility.

191
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,549
But now we're not sure

192
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:43,870
if there are connections
between the nursing home

193
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:45,760
and both Lin Xuehui and her mother.

194
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,120
So, we need to reinvestigate

195
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,390
these victims' interpersonal relations.

196
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:48,870
Understood?

197
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,630
Understood.

198
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:50,330
Get to work.

199
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,420
Take a nap if you're tired.

200
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,400
Newcomers to the Police Station

201
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:40,290
usually find it hard to settle in.

202
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,490
I'm actually...

203
00:09:42,970 --> 00:09:43,910
I'm actually adjusting well.

204
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:44,790
I can manage.

205
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,000
Look into this.

206
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,450
Okay. Just a moment.

207
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,580
Lu Yizhen, pull yourself together.

208
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:03,020
Dong.

209
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:04,840
Do you have anything

210
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,670
that can refresh my mind?

211
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,540
Something refreshing...

212
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:11,800
A cup of coffee.

213
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:14,950
I've had cups of coffee.

214
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:16,480
I can't drink that anymore.

215
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,840
Why not go home and get some sleep?

216
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,570
This is going to be a long night.

217
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,990
How are you still so energetic?

218
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,710
Me?

219
00:10:31,910 --> 00:10:33,870
After working for many years
in the police station,

220
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:35,800
I've got used to this work pattern.

221
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,680
You're new here.

222
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,510
It's understandable
that you haven't adjusted to it.

223
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:40,370
Just take a nap.

224
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:43,780
Maybe I should resort to drastic measures.

225
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:48,690
I forgot a document.

226
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,810
Get some sleep. It won't affect anything.

227
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:31,960
Inspector,

228
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:34,870
why not just let her go?

229
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,750
It'll take her several hours on the road
if she leaves now.

230
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,950
All that time will be wasted traveling.

231
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,730
That's true.

232
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,080
Besides, she said she could adjust

233
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,680
and continue reading files.

234
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,090
Go ahead with your work.

235
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,150
Be gentle.

236
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,200
Hello?

237
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,890
This is the Police Station.

238
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,390
You're asking for Lu Yizhen?

239
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:29,450
Okay, please hold.

240
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:31,390
Lu Yizhen.

241
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,840
Lu Yizhen!

242
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:35,530
A call for you.

243
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,390
Thanks.

244
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,400
Hello, this is Lu Yizhen.

245
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,600
Mrs. Gao?

246
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,130
Okay. I'll be right there.

247
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,370
What happened?

248
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,660
It was a call from Fang Ruhai.

249
00:12:57,660 --> 00:12:58,750
He said Mrs. Gao was at his place.

250
00:12:58,750 --> 00:12:59,600
But she got sick,

251
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,720
and he couldn't send her back,
so he asked me to come over.

252
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,980
Any doubts about that?

253
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:07,390
Fang works for the China International
Famine Relief Commission.

254
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:08,360
This institute

255
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,440
has rendered help
to the nursing home before.

256
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,200
He could've asked

257
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,630
a colleague of his to send Mrs. Gao back.

258
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,430
Why did he call me in particular?

259
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:16,630
I'll go with you.

260
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:17,270
No need.

261
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,160
Maybe I'm overthinking it.

262
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:20,550
Dong,

263
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,790
in our files, is there information

264
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:23,600
about the China International
Famine Relief Commission?

265
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,530
I feel like I've seen it somewhere.

266
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,140
I'm looking for it.

267
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,650
Alright.

268
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:29,740
I'm leaving now.

269
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,160
It's a chance to investigate Fang Ruhai.

270
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:31,640
Dong,

271
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,150
go with Lu Yizhen.

272
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,210
I'll do the search.

273
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:35,600
Hurry up.

274
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:38,130
Okay, fine.

275
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:47,600
I thought

276
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,470
Officer Lu would come alone.

277
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:52,270
With the two of us here,

278
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:54,530
Mrs. Gao's safety can be better secured.

279
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,570
Where is she?

280
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:56,510
Come on in.

281
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,480
